## Common Commands

```bash
npm run chrome:debug        # launch Chrome with debugging on :9222 (required before agent runs)
npm run dev                 # API (4177) + dashboard (5173)
npm run agent:once          # one full pipeline pass
npm run agent:loop          # continuous loop every 90s
npm run mode -- review      # safe mode (propose only)
npm run mode -- auto        # live mode (sends replies)
npm run mode -- paused      # stop automation
npm run data:prepare-live   # reset to clean review state
npm run simulate            # seeded test scenarios
npm run build               # tsc + vite build (use npx tsc --noEmit for type check only)
```

